      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "PAW BRUTUS (4) is a talented type and proved too classy last time to win by a neck at The Meadows in a handy 30.04 beating Brave Island. Winner at his latest appearance in one of the quickest times on the card. Well placed and can measure up. ALL I SEE (5) slotted in just off the lead from the wide box before lifting strongly to score (29.97) at this track in a Maiden over 515m. Must be included in calculations. BIG WATCH (3) broke a string of placings finishing in the money two on end before a last start fourth (35.09) at this track. A big run wouldn't surprise. MIKADO MANIA (2) comes off a (19.38) win last time, scoring by 6 lengths in a T3 Grade 6 over 350m at Healesville. Has already won out of this draw.",
